avasara kalyanam ( தமிழ் : அவசரக் கல்யாணம் , english : urgent marriage ) is a 1972 black-and-white tamil comedy family film was directed by v. t. thyagarajan and produced by subalakshmi movies .   the film script were written by bala murugan .   music by t. r. pappa assets to the movie .   the film starring jaishankar and nagesh played lead role with vanisri rama prabha and v. k. ramasamy portraying supporting roles .